sition=\"top\" spacer_img_width=\"48\" line_style=\"solid\" line_height=\"1\" line_color=\"#333333\" icon_type=\"selector\" icon=\"\" icon_size=\"32\" icon_color=\"\" icon_style=\"none\" icon_color_bg=\"\" icon_border_style=\"\" icon_color_border=\"#333333\" icon_border_size=\"1\" icon_border_radius=\"500\" icon_border_spacing=\"50\" icon_img=\"\" img_width=\"48\" line_icon_fixer=\"10\" main_heading_font_family=\"font_family:Montserrat|font_call:Montserrat|variant:700\" main_heading_style=\"font-weight:700;\" main_heading_font_size=\"desktop:18px;\" main_heading_line_height=\"desktop:30px;\" main_heading_margin=\"margin-bottom:30px;\"][/ultimate_heading][vc_column_text css_animation=\"\"] The BCI Breakfast Program focuses on providing a balanced and nourishing breakfast. Each child is provided a whole grain bun, a protein (meat, egg or peanut butter) and a piece of fresh fruit. Less than 50¢ a day will provide a child with the fuel they need to succeed in school.\r\n\r\nWe were well aware of the need for a Breakfast Program at the BCI Academy and we had spent several months discussing how to go about doing it. One day, we just decided to go for it and do a “trial run” with 14 of the neediest children, as selected and agreed upon by the teachers and social workers.\r\n\r\nThe reports we received about the children in the trial run was astounding. The teachers were amazed by how much better the children were doing in class. Not only were they more alert but their grades improved and they were far more interactive and involved. The teachers were so excited to see their students like this and asked us to keep this program going. After seeing the impact this Breakfast Program has, how could we say no?\r\n\r\nThe Breakfast program was started in 2010 and has since quadrupled in the number of children being fed each morning.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"\" width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"1031\" alignment=\"center\" style=\"\" bor