INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1112", "1", "2015-10-31 10:34:23", "2015-10-31 10:34:23", "[vc_row centered=\"yes\" bg_type=\"image\" parallax_style=\"vcpb-default\" bg_image_new=\"33|http://helpinghands.skat.tf/wp-content/uploads/sites/14/edd/2015/07/campaign-title-bg.jpg\" bg_image_repeat=\"no-repeat\"][vc_column][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row centered=\"yes\"][vc_column][ultimate_spacer height=\"70\"][ultimate_heading main_heading=\"THE NEED\" alignment=\"left\"][/ultimate_heading][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row centered=\"yes\" sd_margin_top=\"70px\"][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][ultimate_heading sub_heading_color=\"#ffffff\" alignment=\"left\" sub_heading_font_family=\"font_family:Montserrat|font_call:Montserrat|variant:700\" sub_heading_style=\"font-weight:700;\" sub_heading_font_size=\"desktop:12px;\" sub_heading_line_height=\"desktop:12px;\" sub_heading_margin=\"margin-bottom:20px;\"]\n<p class=\"sd-text-background\">GETTING TO KNOW ETHIOPIA</p>\n[/ultimate_heading][ultimate_heading sub_heading_color=\"#435061\" alignment=\"left\" sub_heading_font_family=\"font_family:Montserrat|font_call:Montserrat|variant:700\" sub_heading_style=\"font-weight:700;\" sub_heading_font_size=\"desktop:24px;\" sub_heading_line_height=\"desktop:36px;\" sub_heading_margin=\"margin-bottom:20px;\"]WE ARE HELPING HANDS[/ultimate_heading][vc_column_text]Located in Northeast Africa, Ethiopia is a mostly mountainous landscape with scattered deserts in the lowlands. Ethiopia continues to lag behind in developing as a nation making death rates and life expectancy well below the world average. Here are a few facts about Ethiopia:\n<ul>\n	<li>Capital:  Addis Ababa</li>\n	<li>Population: 99 Million</li>\n	<li>Currency:  Ethiopian Birr</li>\n	<li>Official Language:  Amharic</li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][ultimate_spacer height=\"10\"][ultimate_info_table design_style=\"design02\" color_scheme=\"blue\" package_heading=\"Ethiopia compared to the United States\"]\n<table class=\"comparison-table\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td> <strong>Topic</strong></td>\n<td><strong>Ethiopia</strong></td>\n<td><strong>United States</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Illiteracy Rate</td>\n<td>50.9%</td>\n<td>&lt;1%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Life Expectancy</td>\n<td>61 Years</td>\n<td>79 Years</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Infant Mortality Rate</td>\n<td>5.337%</td>\n<td>.058%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>GNP Per Capita</td>\n<td>$550</td>\n<td>$55,200</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Unemployment</td>\n<td>17.5%</td>\n<td>5.5%</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n[/ultimate_info_table][ultimate_spacer height=\"10\"][ultimate_spacer height=\"10\"][ultimate_heading sub_heading_color=\"#435061\" alignment=\"left\" sub_heading_font_family=\"font_family:Montserrat|font_call:Montserrat|variant:700\" sub_heading_style=\"font-weight:700;\" sub_heading_font_size=\"desktop:24px;\" sub_heading_line_height=\"desktop:36px;\" sub_heading_margin=\"margin-bottom:20px;\"]HOW YOU CAN HELP[/ultimate_heading][vc_column_text]<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-617 alignleft\" src=\"http://griffin.technicalbd.com/customer/griffin/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/boy-and-his-axe-279x300.jpg\" alt=\"boy and his axe\" width=\"279\" height=\"300\" />The dismal economic situation of Ethiopia drastically impacts the country\'s children. Millions of Ethiopian children are forced to literally live in garbage as they rummage for food in the city dumps. But we believe their fate can change.\n\nAt Blessing The Children International, we want to provide you with the ability to change the future of these children. By sponsoring a child, they will receive food, education, and learn about the difference Jesus can make in their lives.\n\nWhen you decide to partner with us, it means so much more than just writing us a check. You are helping Ethiopian children start a new life–a life where they are fed, where they are educated, and where they are taught that God loves them more than anyone.[/vc_column_text][ultimate_spacer height=\"10\"][ult_buttons btn_title=\"DONATE NOW\" btn_link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Fhelpinghands.skat.tf%2Four-causes%2F|title:Donate%20Now|\" btn_size=\"ubtn-custom\" btn_width=\"190\" btn_height=\"45\" btn_title_color=\"#ffffff\" btn_bg_color=\"#0f47af\" btn_hover=\"ubtn-fade-bg\" btn_bg_color_hover=\"#2dc69b\" icon_size=\"32\" btn_icon_pos=\"ubtn-sep-icon-at-left\" btn_border_style=\"solid\" btn_border_size=\"0\" btn_radius=\"3\" btn_font_family=\"font_family:Montserrat|font_call:Montserrat\" btn_font_style=\"font-weight:bold;\" btn_font_size=\"13\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][ultimate_heading sub_heading_color=\"#ffffff\" alignment=\"left\" sub_heading_font_family=\"font_family:Montserrat|font_call:Montserrat|variant:700\" sub_heading_style=\"font-weight:700;\" sub_heading_font_size=\"desktop:12px;\" sub_heading_line_height=\"desktop:12px;\" sub_heading_margin=\"margin-bottom:20px;\"]\n<p class=\"sd-text-background\">DID YOU KNOW?</p>\n[/ultimate_heading][ultimate_heading sub_heading_color=\"#435061\" alignment=\"left\" sub_heading_font_family=\"font_family:Montserrat|font_call:Montserrat|variant:700\" sub_heading_style=\"font-weight:700;\" sub_heading_font_size=\"desktop:24px;\" sub_heading_line_height=\"desktop:36px;\" sub_heading_margin=\"margin-bottom:20px;\"]INTERESTING FACTS ABOUT ETHIOPIA[/ultimate_heading][vc_column_text]With an estimated population of 86 million people, 78% of Ethiopians struggle with an income below US$2 a day.\n\nThe State Health expenditure is approximately $3 per person in Ethiopia.\n\nPreventable diseases, including Malaria, account for at least 60% of health problems in the country.[/vc_column_text][ultimate_heading sub_heading_color=\"#435061\" alignment=\"left\" sub_heading_font_family=\"font_family:Montserrat|font_call:Montserrat|variant:700\" sub_heading_style=\"font-weight:700;\" sub_heading_font_size=\"desktop:24px;\" sub_heading_line_height=\"desktop:36px;\" sub_heading_margin=\"margin-bottom:20px;\"]THREE WAYS BCI HELPS CHILDREN[/ultimate_heading][just_icon icon=\"Defaults-plus-square\" icon_size=\"36\" icon_color=\"#0f47af\" icon_align=\"left\"][ultimate_heading main_heading=\"1. HEALTH\" heading_tag=\"h3\" alignment=\"left\" main_heading_font_family=\"font_family:Montserrat|font_call:Montserrat|variant:700\" main_heading_style=\"font-weight:700;\" main_heading_font_size=\"desktop:14px;\" main_heading_line_height=\"desktop:14px;\" main_heading_margin=\"margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:15px;\" sub_heading_line_height=\"desktop:24px;\"]Every child needs food, water, and shelter. Most of the kids we work with often hardly have any of these.[/ultimate_heading][ultimate_spacer height=\"10\"][just_icon icon=\"Defaults-pencil\" icon_size=\"36\" icon_color=\"#0f47af\" icon_align=\"left\"][ultimate_heading main_heading=\"2. EDUCATION\" heading_tag=\"h3\" alignment=\"left\" main_heading_font_family=\"font_family:Montserrat|font_call:Montserrat|variant:700\" main_heading_style=\"font-weight:700;\" main_heading_font_size=\"desktop:14px;\" main_heading_line_height=\"desktop:14px;\" main_heading_margin=\"margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:15px;\" sub_heading_line_height=\"desktop:24px;\"]One day, we realize the children we help will grow up. Therefore, we ensure that they receive a high-level education. That\'s why we started the <a href=\"http://griffin.technicalbd.com/customer/griffin/our-team/\">BCI Academy.</a>[/ultimate_heading][ultimate_spacer height=\"10\"][just_icon icon=\"Defaults-power-off\" icon_size=\"36\" icon_color=\"#0f47af\" icon_align=\"left\"][ultimate_heading main_heading=\"3. FAITH\" heading_tag=\"h3\" alignment=\"left\" main_heading_font_family=\"font_family:Montserrat|font_call:Montserrat|variant:700\" main_heading_style=\"font-weight:700;\" main_heading_font_size=\"desktop:14px;\" main_heading_line_height=\"desktop:14px;\" main_heading_margin=\"margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:15px;\" sub_heading_line_height=\"desktop:24px;\"]We take joy in sharing with these children how deep God\'s love is for each of them. To love God and know God, in our minds, is the greatest of needs.[/ultimate_heading][ultimate_spacer height=\"10\"][vc_images_carousel images=\"621,619,620\" img_size=\"medium\" autoplay=\"yes\" hide_prev_next_buttons=\"yes\" wrap=\"yes\"][/vc_column][vc_column][/vc_column][/vc_row]", "The Need", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "514-autosave-v1", "", "", "2015-10-31 10:34:23", "2015-10-31 10:34:23", "", "514", "http://griffin.technicalbd.com/customer/griffin/2015/10/31/514-autosave-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
